:: Public Holidays
: New Year's Day
"Новий Рік"                                                         weekend on january 1
: New Year's Day Substitute Holiday
"Новий Рік"                                                         weekend on ( (([january 1] == [saturday after ([january 1])]) ||
                                                                                  ([january 1] == [sunday after ([january 1])])) ?
                                                                                      [monday after ([january 1])] :
                                                                                  noop )
